Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/aherrmann/dotfiles.git ~/.dotfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the ~/.dotfiles directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/.dotfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update


Useful aliases

    git config alias.addvimbundlelocal \!"sh -c 'git add vim/bundle/\"\$1\" && git commit -m \"Installed $1 bundle\"' -"
    git config alias.addvimbundle \!"sh -c 'git submodule add \"\$1\" vim/bundle/\"\$2\" && git config -f .gitmodules submodule.vim/bundle/\"\$2\".ignore dirty && git commit -m \"Installed \$2 bundle as a submodule\"' -"
